t\in \text{span} S
t=\sum_{i=1}^n a_i u_i = \sum_{j=1}^m b_j v_j
n=m, a_i=b_i
u_i=v_i
0=t-t=\sum_{\lambda\in\Lambda} a_{\lambda}u_{\lambda}-\sum_{\lambda\in\Lambda} b_{\lambda}u_{\lambda}=\sum_{\lambda\in\Lambda} (a_{\lambda}-b_{\lambda})u_{\lambda}
(a_{\lambda}-b_{\lambda})=0
